&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end creative workflow, from intake through delivery, ensuring clarity, efficiency, and accountability at every stage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enforce and manage a centralized intake process through Wrike; ensure all work is properly submitted, scoped, and prioritized&lt;/li&gt;
